The Upside of Anger;;2005;;R;;Comedy,Drama;;6.8;;Mike Binder;;Joan Allen,Kevin Costner,Erika Christensen,Evan Rachel Wood,Keri Russell,Alicia Witt,Mike Binder,Tom Harper,Dane Christensen,Danny Webb,Magdalena Manville,Suzanne Bertish,David Firth,Rod Woodruff,Stephen Greif,Arthur Penhallow,Richard Mylan,Robert Perkins;;A sharp-witted suburban wife, Terry Wolfmeyer, is left to raise her four headstrong daughters when her husband unexpectedly disappears. Things get even more hectic when she falls for her neighbor Denny, a once-great baseball star turned radio d.j. This leaves her daughters out on a limb. They are forced to juggle their mom's romantic dilemmas as well as their own.;;https://www.imdb.com/title/tt0365885/